在[[物理宇宙學|宇宙学]]中，'''暗物質'''（{{lang-en|Dark Matter}}）是指不與[[电磁力|电磁力]]產生作用的物质，也就是不會吸收、反射或發出[[光|光]]。人们目前只能透过[[重力|重力]]产生的效应得知，而且已經發现[[宇宙|宇宙]]中有大量暗物质的存在。<ref name="CERN Dark Matter">{{cite web |url=http://home.cern/about/physics/dark-matter |title=Dark Matter |website=CERN Physics |date=20 January 2012 |accessdate=2016-05-30 |archive-date=2016-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160604121500/http://home.cern/about/physics/dark-matter |dead-url=no }}</ref>

现代天文学經由[[引力透镜|引力透镜]]、宇宙中[[大尺度结构|大尺度结构]]的形成、[[微波背景辐射|微波背景辐射]]等方法和理论来探测暗物质。而根据[[ΛCDM模型|ΛCDM模型]]，由[[普朗克卫星|普朗克卫星]]探测的数据得到：整个宇宙的构成中，常規物質（即[[重子|重子]][[物質|物質]]）占4.9%，而暗物质則占26.8%，还有68.3%是[[暗能量|暗能量]]（[[质能等价|质能等价]]）。<ref name="planck_overview">{{cite journal |url=http://arxiv.org/pdf/1303.5062v1.pdf |title=Planck 2013 results. I. Overview of products and scientific results – Table 9. |journal=[[Astronomy_and_Astrophysics|Astronomy and Astrophysics]] ''(submitted)'' |first1=P. A. R. |last1=Ade |first2=N. |last2=Aghanim |first3=C. |last3=Armitage-Caplan |last4=''et al''. (Planck Collaboration) |date=22 March 2013 |arxiv=1303.5062 |access-date=2013-05-01 |archive-date=2015-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150904005725/http://arxiv.org/pdf/1303.5062v1.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="planck_overview2">{{cite journal |url=http://www.sciops.esa.int/index.php?project=PLANCK&page=Planck_Published_Papers |title=Planck 2013 Results Papers |journal=[[Astronomy_and_Astrophysics|Astronomy and Astrophysics]] ''(submitted)'' |first1=P. A. R. |last1=Ade |first2=N. |last2=Aghanim |first3=C. |last3=Armitage-Caplan |last4=''et al''. (Planck Collaboration) |date=31 March 2013 |arxiv=1303.5062 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130323234553/http://www.sciops.esa.int/index.php?project=PLANCK&page=Planck_Published_Papers |archivedate=2013年3月23日 }}</ref><ref name="wmap7parameters">{{cite web|title = First Planck results: the Universe is still weird and interesting|url = http://arstechnica.com/science/2013/03/first-planck-results-the-universe-is-still-weird-and-interesting/|accessdate = 2013-05-01|archive-date = 2015-08-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150818001309/http://arstechnica.com/science/2013/03/first-planck-results-the-universe-is-still-weird-and-interesting/|dead-url = no}}</ref>暗物质的存在可以解决[[大爆炸理论|大爆炸理论]]中的不自洽性（inconsistency），对结构形成也非常关键。暗物质很有可能是一种（或几种）[[粒子物理|粒子物理]][[标准模型|标准模型]]以外的新粒子所構成。对暗物质（和暗能量）的研究是现代[[宇宙学|宇宙学]]和[[粒子物理|粒子物理]]的重要课题。

2015年11月，NASA[[噴射推進實驗室|噴射推進實驗室]]的科學家蓋瑞·普里茲奧（Gary Prézeau）以[[ΛCDM模型|ΛCDM模型]]模擬銀河系內暗物質流過地球與木星等行星的情形，發現這會使該暗物質流的密度明顯上升（地球：<math>10^7</math>倍、木星：<math>10^8</math>倍），並呈現毛髮狀的向外輻射分佈結構<ref>{{cite journal|title=Dense Dark Matter Hairs Spreading Out from Earth, Jupiter and Other Compact Bodies|author=Gary Prézeau|arxiv=1507.07009|journal=The Astrophysical Journal|date=2015-11-25|accessdate=2015-11-27|url=http://inspirehep.net/record/1385057}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Earth Might Have Hairy Dark Matter|url=https://www.nasa.gov/feature/jpl/earth-might-have-hairy-dark-matter|date=2015-11-24|author=Elizabeth Landau|publisher=NASA's Jet Propulsion Laboratory|accessdate=2015-11-27|archive-date=2015-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151127112111/https://www.nasa.gov/feature/jpl/earth-might-have-hairy-dark-matter/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

